00:17:02,262 --> 00:17:04,306
You wouldn't know about that.

246
00:17:04,473 --> 00:17:06,558
- Niles.
- You don't know how to behave.

247
00:17:06,725 --> 00:17:09,227
You don't know
the meaning of rectitude.

