277
00:20:27,674 --> 00:20:30,468
- My shoes?
- Yes, l'm sorry.

278
00:20:31,636 --> 00:20:34,264
Apparently, l mistranslated.

279
00:20:34,431 --> 00:20:38,685
He didn't mean... Not shoes, wife.

280
00:20:39,602 --> 00:20:41,646
